modName: Fast Map Travel from INSIDE your House
summary:
This addons make fast travel from inside your house possible.
It works with all the houses that you can buy in game.
Soon I\'ll add also the rooms avaible as quest reward( College of Winterhold, Companions etc.)
If you like it please vote and subscribe. Thanks.

Debz
descriptionHtml:
Bored to have to go out, when you are in your house chilling with Lydia, in order to begin your next adventure?
This addons make fast travel from inside your house possible.
It works with all the houses that you can buy in game.
Soon I\'ll add also the rooms avaible as quest reward( College of Winterhold, Companions etc.)
If you like it please vote and subscribe. Thanks.

Debz

HOW TO: 
DownloadManual: Copy the data folder in your Skyrim folder and load the game.
DownloadManager: just click and download. 
(if there is any problem just write it in the comment, I ll fix it)
author: Debz
